Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.00,0:00:17.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,創界山再次出現了危機
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.80,0:00:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由於連接魔界與神部界的大門被打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.10,0:00:23.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,創界山產生了巨大的崩壞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.24,0:00:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔界的魔物也陸續來襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.10,0:00:27.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要想關閉大門的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.80,0:00:31.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有拿到天部界的"劍龍之勾玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.70,0:00:35.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 天部界是我們不能接近的世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.42,0:00:40.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使如此 為了拯救神部界也不得不去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.10,0:00:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(400,350)}—\h沒有終結之時的物語\h—
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.00,0:01:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(300,2000)}天部界之嵐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.13,0:01:37.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡就是天部界?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.43,0:01:39.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.64,0:01:46.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我還以為是個更壯觀的地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.32,0:01:48.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別說得這麼輕鬆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.32,0:01:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我說 關於"劍龍之勾玉" 還是問問別人比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.84,0:01:55.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,問誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.55,0:01:59.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道"劍龍之勾玉"在哪嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.00,0:02:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是不知道才要這樣向前走啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.25,0:02:07.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,問問大龍光帝吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.20,0:02:08.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是天部界的國王吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.32,0:02:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那大龍光帝在哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.51,0:02:18.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來只能邊走邊找了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.26,0:02:22.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是神部界的人是禁止進入天部界的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:22.82,0:02:25.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想大龍光帝也不會見我們的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.02,0:02:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就碰碰運氣吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.00,0:02:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是魔界的魔神嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.21,0:02:48.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是你說要碰運氣的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.55,0:02:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你好 那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.34,0:02:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們是為了拿到"劍龍之勾玉"而從神部界來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.09,0:03:01.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神部界來的!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.87,0:03:02.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,啊 是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.25,0:03:05.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你們以為這裡是哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.36,0:03:10.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放開我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:11.95,0:03:17.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這裡可是禁止神部界的人進入的天部界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.94,0:03:19.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神部界有危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.10,0:03:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔界的人正要把通向神部界之門打開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.37,0:03:25.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.93,0:03:30.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管怎樣 也不容許闖入天部界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.71,0:03:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無名小卒 看我把你們捏個粉碎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.09,0:03:37.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們才不是無名小卒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.30,0:03:39.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快放開海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.88,0:03:43.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大膽傢伙 想與天部界對抗嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.75,0:03:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就讓你嘗嘗天罰的滋味吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.90,0:03:53.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.35,0:04:20.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是天部界的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.30,0:04:25.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡可是從魔界之人手中拯救神部界的救世主啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.29,0:04:28.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,住口
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.71,0:04:29.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.81,0:04:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救世主…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.70,0:04:34.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看來神部界已淪落到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.66,0:04:37.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不得不由這樣的小孩來保護呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.97,0:04:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.20,0:04:41.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,四天龍王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,四天龍王…天部界的神子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.48,0:04:48.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,想要"劍龍之勾玉"嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.60,0:04:51.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我在問你是不是想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.50,0:04:54.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在此之前 先放了海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.13,0:05:02.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你想命令我嗎!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.00,0:05:04.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我並不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.02,0:05:09.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,修羅童子和霸翔童子是天部界的守門人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.56,0:05:13.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要我一聲令下 他就會沒命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.16,0:05:19.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快跪地求饒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.05,0:05:27.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.36,0:05:31.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們並沒有做壞事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.00,0:05:36.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只是來拜託你門協助拯救神部界的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.68,0:05:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,無論如何都需要"劍龍之勾玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:40.10,0:05:43.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,請你告訴我"劍龍之勾玉"在什麼地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.35,0:05:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吧 我就告訴你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.40,0:05:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"劍龍之勾玉"就在由此向南越過兩百座山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.78,0:06:03.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,兩百個湖 兩百座森林的玄聖山那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.53,0:06:04.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玄聖山?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.90,0:06:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,憑你的雙腳要花上多少年呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:08.70,0:06:10.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼說是來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.30,0:06:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果是這匹麟王 只要一飛就能到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.95,0:06:17.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎樣 要搶走麟王嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.88,0:06:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.67,0:06:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算是搶也要試一試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.54,0:06:25.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.70,0:06:38.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光龍劍被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:39.70,0:06:43.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就讓我看看拯救神部界的救世主的力量吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.80,0:06:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要不被修羅童子和霸翔童子抓到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.50,0:06:51.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,並拿到那把劍的話 就讓你騎麟王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.02,0:07:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可惡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.20,0:07:24.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幹得好 渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.10,0:07:39.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.21,0:07:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神部界的救世主就只有這點能耐嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:00.30,0:08:01.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:05.30,0:08:07.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到此為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.90,0:08:53.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在見到"劍龍之勾玉"之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.30,0:08:56.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救世主渡 你就會死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.52,0:09:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在這前面有操縱龍的一族
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.89,0:09:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"劍龍之勾玉"就在那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.50,0:09:15.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:17.40,0:09:20.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只憑我們可能拿不到"劍龍之勾玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.20,0:09:22.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,能不能請你也一起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.04,0:09:24.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別得意忘形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.10,0:09:28.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,光是讓神部界的你們活著 你們就該感恩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.95,0:09:30.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.10,0:09:36.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,帶我們到這裡真是莫大的幫助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.82,0:09:39.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼讓他回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.34,0:09:48.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既然是天部界的神子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.72,0:09:52.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,說不定能讓操龍之族立刻交出"劍龍之勾玉"啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.63,0:09:55.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,或許是這樣 但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.81,0:09:58.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更重要的是 我們怎麼回去啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.10,0:10:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,總之 先去那個山谷看看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.25,0:10:02.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.53,0:10:33.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好厲害啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.34,0:10:39.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好像…有種不可思議的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.51,0:10:45.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,似乎很久以前曾經來過這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.65,0:10:48.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哪有可能啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.91,0:10:49.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你說得對 可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.94,0:10:51.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先別說了 口很渴了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.35,0:10:58.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.60,0:11:00.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.20,0:11:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奧璐 放下刀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.30,0:11:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"劍龍之勾玉"是千年一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.48,0:11:25.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,龍之王者劍龍從天而降時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.44,0:11:27.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才會在這裡出現的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.54,0:11:28.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,千年一次!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.70,0:11:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同時 我們龍之一族會誕生一個嬰兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.00,0:11:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"劍龍之勾玉"就會變成那孩子的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.52,0:11:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那現在"劍龍之勾玉"就在這裡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:47.49,0:11:49.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們沒有時間啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.31,0:11:52.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到底有沒有 快告訴我們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.80,0:11:53.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.83,0:11:58.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"劍龍之勾玉"是千年前前往遙遠世界的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.36,0:12:00.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劍龍士的生命化成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劍龍士?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.26,0:12:14.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在 新的劍龍士就快誕生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 劍龍就會從天而降嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.93,0:12:21.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了 那就可以拿到"劍龍之勾玉"了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.79,0:12:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.79,0:12:25.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"劍龍之勾玉"是龍劍士的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.50,0:12:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能給你們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.20,0:12:30.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我們非救神部界不可啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:34.25,0:12:35.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是劍龍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.85,0:12:40.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劍龍從天而降了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:08.79,0:13:11.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快迎接劍龍降臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.73,0:13:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,點火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.01,0:14:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那就是…劍龍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是不是開始做什麼事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,誕生永遠的生命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永遠的生命…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.60,0:14:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,另一個"無盡"要開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.85,0:14:49.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和你一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,和…和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.70,0:15:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,救世主渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:04.63,0:15:09.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"劍龍之勾玉"可不能那麼輕易讓你得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.25,0:15:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,閻羅王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.66,0:15:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,趁現在快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.45,0:15:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:32.22,0:15:32.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快躲開…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.20,0:15:33.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:38.78,0:15:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快去保護劍龍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Adaru
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.14,0:15:57.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:59.65,0:16:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,沒事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是它的對手 快躲開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.30,0:16:07.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,借來一用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.08,0:16:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你知道這裡是哪裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.50,0:16:17.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:17.40,0:16:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是救世主的出生地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.55,0:16:22.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是你的故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.30,0:16:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,同時也是你的葬身之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.26,0:16:28.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,看招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.58,0:17:14.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劍龍…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.45,0:17:23.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劍龍…在哭?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:18.58,0:18:23.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劍龍的…嬰兒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.52,0:18:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這是"劍龍之勾玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.70,0:18:47.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,休想得到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.10,0:18:49.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,死吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.00,0:18:59.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劍被…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.84,0:19:06.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,休想逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.20,0:19:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.86,0:19:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這麼一來神部界就屬於我們魔界的了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.44,0:19:38.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吼鬼 把劍龍和救世主一起埋葬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.13,0:19:44.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,危險
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.70,0:19:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:00.30,0:20:01.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Adaru…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.75,0:20:22.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,四天龍王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.72,0:20:25.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天部界的神子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.70,0:20:29.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我原以為還沒到和你決勝負的時候呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.55,0:20:31.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,邪惡之徒 退下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.50,0:20:38.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毀滅神部界之後就輪到天部界了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.35,0:20:42.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到時再一決勝負吧 四天龍王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.29,0:20:50.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一定會記著的 閻羅王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.20,0:21:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不管怎樣都已經得不到"劍龍之勾玉"了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.15,0:21:09.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼辦 渡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.70,0:21:14.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"劍龍之勾玉"是為了成就救世主的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:15.70,0:21:19.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,千年誕生一次的劍龍士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.87,0:21:22.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是為了完成下一任救世主的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.34,0:21:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,現在的劍龍士 換言之救世主 就是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.83,0:21:33.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"劍龍之勾玉"正由你持有著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:34.58,0:21:40.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你所擁有的"劍龍之勾玉"就能拯救神部界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.69,0:21:43.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我並沒擁有那樣東西 在哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.26,0:21:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就在你的體內
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:46.27,0:21:47.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的體內?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.30,0:21:52.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你就是獲得"劍龍之勾玉"的劍龍士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.70,0:21:56.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,劍龍的孩子!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.38,0:22:27.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:28.52,0:22:30.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為什麼虎王會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.19,0:22:34.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 海火子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:34.50,0:22:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦 本少爺在哪裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.37,0:22:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.78,0:22:44.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,渡 好想見你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.31,0:22:49.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是劍龍將虎王帶回原來的世界了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:49.89,0:22:51.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.49,0:22:53.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,這就是白龍馬嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:53.43,0:22:54.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白龍馬?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:55.05,0:22:56.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白龍的化身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.73,0:23:00.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,為了回報拚命守護龍的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.19,0:23:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白龍就變成這般模樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.20,0:23:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,聽從那個人的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.82,0:23:07.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,白龍它…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:07.79,0:23:10.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,作為保護天部界的獎賞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.48,0:23:12.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我把這匹麟王借給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:13.27,0:23:15.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有這兩匹馬在的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:15.53,0:23:18.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對你們的戰鬥也會有些幫助吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.96,0:23:20.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,非常感謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:25.46,0:23:27.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那麼 我們就回神部界去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:28.33,0:23:30.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,別輸給魔界的那些傢伙啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.60,0:23:32.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎麼會輸呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:32.90,0:23:34.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,奧璐也要保重啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.10,0:23:36.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,干 幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.90,0:23:38.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.77,0:23:42.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,再見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.84,0:23:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Adaru…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:44.66,0:23:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永遠的生命 沒有終結之時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:48.82,0:23:53.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,新誕生的劍龍士已不再是救世主了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:54.40,0:23:58.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,雖然沒有獲得"劍龍之勾玉"
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:58.10,0:24:01.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 卻得到了其代替品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.04,0:24:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是救世主渡 你的心啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.19,0:24:14.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虎王 回到神部界後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.81,0:24:16.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要面臨和魔界之人的戰鬥了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.00,0:24:18.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,包在我身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.66,0:24:20.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 快點走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.43,0:25:13.41,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}耳をふさいでも 聞こえていたの
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.37,0:25:20.58,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}時の砂が落ちる音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.71,0:25:28.92,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}黃昏に金の雲を残して
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.51,0:25:35.72,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}沈む夕陽をせつなく見る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.93,0:25:47.65,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}Adieu 悲しみの 夜は來るけれど
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.94,0:25:51.70,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}淚 見せない
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.99,0:25:55.45,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}永遠の扉を
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.73,0:26:06.92,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}開けば始まる 終わりなき時の物語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.21,0:26:10.88,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}出逢いは一瞬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.09,0:26:14.68,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}でも胸に Memory
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:15.14,0:26:26.44,jpoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,350)}君の熱さを忘れないよ Forever
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.43,0:25:13.41,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}即使堵上耳朵也能聽見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:14.37,0:25:20.58,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}沙漏漏下的聲音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:22.71,0:25:28.92,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}黃昏時只殘留金色的雲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:29.51,0:25:35.72,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}難過的看著夕陽落下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:37.93,0:25:47.65,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}Adieu 悲傷的夜晚到來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:47.94,0:25:51.70,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}卻不讓你看見淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:51.99,0:25:55.45,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}只要開啟永遠的門扉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:55.73,0:26:06.92,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}永恆的傳說就會開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:07.21,0:26:10.88,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}雖然只有瞬間的邂逅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:11.09,0:26:14.68,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,150)}但胸中的 Memory
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:15.14,0:26:26.44,cnoped,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(150,350)}不會忘記你的熱情 Forever
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:54.19,0:26:57.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,神部界失去了神部七龍神的力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:57.37,0:26:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,對魔界的攻擊只能坐以待斃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:26:59.95,0:27:03.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人們都受了傷 不得不退出戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:03.76,0:27:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我和虎王 海火子一起來到通向魔界的大門那裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:08.68,0:27:11.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是 "劍龍之勾玉"並不在我手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:11.95,0:27:15.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,信念 信念就是我最後的戰鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:15.85,0:27:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,永遠的傳說
